gwt.g3d.client.shader
Class AbstractShader

java.lang.Object
  gwt.g3d.client.shader.AbstractShader
All Implemented Interfaces:
GLDisposable, Shader
Direct Known Subclasses:
BasicShader3D, FlatShader, TextureShader
public abstract class AbstractShader
extends java.lang.Object
implements Shader

Represents a WebGL shader. AbstractShader caches the uniform locations and attribute locations, so it is only slow the first time of those values are retrieved.
